textBox.richText: So my first day of Project ONE12, was the day after I celebrated my 24th birthday. Pretty crazy hey?! I think this journey is a great way to celebrate a new year :) My first week of interning brought me to Fotolia, a stock photography company in downtown Calgary that has some inspirational and unique individuals running the business. <-- this is me, my first day. :) I had the weirdest rush of emotions that morning, I was super nervous... because I didn’t really know what I was getting myself into, but I was also super stoked because I was anxious to start working and being busy again!
